Python project for implementing a 3d playground.

Features:
- Rotation
- Translation
- Moving around the camera
- Inserting dots
- Inserting cubes, spheres, cilinders
- Save and Load
- Export to a 2d picture format
- Export to a 3d format
- Import froms other formats

Use pygame

